data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET after having multiple offers once listed and two extensions buyer couldn't get loan approval. Please bring APPROVED buyer. Welcome home to this well maintained gardeners paradise with a POOL! Back yard was a tropical plant nursery and can be an income producer if desired. Fantastic floor plan features 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, with formal living, dining, kitchen, and family room. Interior features include ceramic tile installed on a diagonal, new carpet in bedrooms, new interior paint, ceiling fans, custom blinds, and updated master bath. Kitchen features include white cabinets, window above sink area, granite counter tops, nook, and pantry. Exterior features include new driveway and sidewalk, large screened lanai, brick exterior, oversized 2 car garage, and fenced rear yard. yard.
